      <description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve not checked in for a long time but let me briefly let you know what I&amp;rsquo;ve been up to.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m testing the new Ubuntu release of Karmic Koala. It is in beta now and should be released at the end of October.
Unfortunately I&amp;rsquo;m away on holiday in Thailand when it comes out so I wanted to have a little play around before I went.
And I&amp;rsquo;ve already raised three bug reports on &lt;a href=&#34;https://launchpad.net/&#34;&gt;Launchpad&lt;/a&gt; already. Minor difficulties but overall
